  UBvo is Un_Bureau_de_vote_S (UTer),
  UFra is Un_Francais_S (URac, UOri, URel, UTer),
  UCet is Un_Conseiller_d_etat_S (URac, UOri, URel, UTer),
  UPre is Un_Prefet_S (URac, UOri, URel, UTer),
  UHfo is Un_Haut_fonctionnaire_S (URac, UOri, URel, UTer),
  UCel is Un_Citoyen_electeur_S (URac, UOri, URel, UTer, UScr, UBvo),
